main.title: S920S00
main.text: Powered by 2 Huawei Kunpeng 920 processors (5220 or 3210) and 1 Hi1710 intelligent management chip, this server board supports up to 16 DDR4-2933 DIMMs and 8 PCIe 4.0 slots, making it ideal for 2U or 4U rack server chassis.
